        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>追求</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2009年7月以前<br>
仰望苍穹席九州，<br>
俯观品类尽自由，<br>
一瓣心香淡如她，<br>
蓦然回首败不休，</p>
<p>乘风破浪寻追求，<br>
荆棘密布练春秋,<br>
光阴雕磨志不变，<br>
青山依旧永长久。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>离别(其一)</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2009年7月21日<br>
昨夜离别今日寒，<br>
东风无力百花残。<br>
一瓣馨香淡如她，<br>
相见时欢别亦难。<br>
独上高山永无怨，<br>
一览众山在心间。<br>
少年壮志不言愁，<br>
敢教日月换新天。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>离别(其二)</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2009年7月21日<br>
一日离别两无言，<br>
雨水洒遍天地间。<br>
燕叫春回头不回，<br>
一心愿为耀天边。<br>
倾城倾国梦期盼，<br>
柔璐发丝绕双眸。<br>
鹰击苍穹冲霄汉，<br>
千载谁堪伯仲间。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>沁园春  中华魂</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2009年10月1日<br>
洪涛东去，<br>
汹涌澎湃，<br>
雪浪滔天。<br>
忆昔年往事，<br>
不禁慨叹。<br>
列强侵华，<br>
撼我江山。<br>
火烧园林，<br>
屠杀千万，<br>
中华儿女痛且坚。<br>
望天边，<br>
那晓岸将辉，<br>
红日送暖。</p>
<p>曾记神州大地，<br>
春风吹遍，<br>
生机盎然。<br>
看华夏儿女，<br>
意气风发；<br>
同甘共苦，<br>
重整河山。<br>
改革开放，<br>
一国两制，<br>
书宏图巨篇。<br>
放未来，<br>
炎黄子孙顶，<br>
兴我家园。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——赠予中华人民共和国诞辰六十周年<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>奋斗</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2019年12月13日<br>
黑夜，摸索着黎明前行，<br>
远方的星光，是否为日出而探路?<br>
古老的长城，沉静的宫殿，<br>
山间的林荫，城中的小巷。<br>
是黑暗？是轮廓？是影子？是光明？<br>
金色的光茫以洒遍神州大地，<br>
新世纪的中国正巍峨屹立于世界东方。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>去最远的地方</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2010年2月2日<br>
时间走得很急，猛然转身。<br>
摇曳的影子在风中徘徊。<br>
未知的未来，<br>
无需谁来编排。<br>
梦想的色彩，期待主宰，<br>
不必信守涂改，<br>
生活依然多姿多彩。<br>
易逝的韶华轻浮脸颊，<br>
享受烟雨中的漫步，<br>
等待晴天时的扬帆远航。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>思</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2010年2月19日<br>
回忆，让我们沉思。<br>
而无边的寂寥，让我们多了一份宁静与清明。<br>
也许，<br>
在远方的你，<br>
有着相同的感受与希望。</p>
<p>时光回溯到以前的夜晚，<br>
幽远的星空依旧绚丽夺目，<br>
久久望着它，<br>
眼前浮现出清晰的画面，<br>
你的声音在那飘渺的烟雾中回响。</p>
<p>只有文字能寄托无奈，<br>
望着你远去的背影，<br>
消失在地平线的尽头。<br>
猛然转身，<br>
荒凉的田野等待雨露的浇灌。</p>
<p>行人的足迹是那么错综复杂。<br>
寻觅着你的足迹，<br>
憧憬发现后的喜悦。<br>
期待，摸索，希望，<br>
编织出相见时的桥梁。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>震动</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2010年5月1日<br>
梦回昨天，心亦沉，天色明转灰。<br>
风啸长空，黄沙卷，难见落英飞。<br>
春回大地，地微颤，玉树化为悲。<br>
天意无情，顷刻间，狼籍涟洏飞。</p>
<p>细听周围，生命脆，脉搏弱而微。<br>
八方亲友，筑信念，冲破砖石垒。<br>
缕缕檀香，酒满杯，祭奠亡灵泪。<br>
看罢疮痍，齐协力，共创家园美。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>  </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——纪念玉树地震<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>星空</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2010年7月24日<br>
极目苍穹，星月轮，斗转随星移。<br>
天之涯，地之角，谁可与心齐。<br>
晨星炫目，焕碧空，若近即离。<br>
此景此理，道似无形却有形，时人知宜。<br>
华夏大地，风云涌，枝芽屹立。<br>
看我东方巨龙，惊天地，腾空而起。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>我与你的距离</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2010年10月2日<br>
有一个身影，日落了还彷徨。<br>
无数个梦在心底激荡，<br>
天空如碧波荡漾。<br>
我与你的距离，似乎是翘首相望。</p>
<p>人海茫茫，<br>
寻找自己的模样，<br>
我与你的距离，是那样模糊而绵长。</p>
<p>曾记你，轻轻唱，<br>
路很长，<br>
风当作我飞翔的希望，<br>
天使的翅膀，为你带来无尽的力量。</p>
<p>空中的楼阁，海中的蜃景，<br>
企图使你迷失方向，<br>
细听我的声响，找回自己的芬芳。<br>
行走的步调正激昂，<br>
带上行囊，愿你一路飞翔。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>眺望</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2011年元月<br>
当我眺望天边，<br>
似乎听到了晨曦的呢喃。<br>
欢呼，雀跃。<br>
又为春的来临祁盼。<br>
时间的步调是那样轻健，<br>
眼前的霞光顷刻不见。<br>
我呆望着天边，<br>
只有夕阳的余辉撒满金山。</p>
<p>试图倒转再现，<br>
但我无能为力。<br>
沉默的誓言，<br>
是否还能力挽狂澜。<br>
哦！不用。<br>
时间是会变化多端。<br>
只留下我，<br>
将期待新的明天！<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>问天</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2011年2月<br>
忆九天神舟，<br>
怀今古，<br>
舜尧谁数？<br>
故地离兮，<br>
往事风华注砥柱，<br>
梦断苍穹旧路。<br>
聚万里，<br>
浮云归属。<br>
天意一向高难问，<br>
人情似，<br>
冷暖秋风处。<br>
同折柳，<br>
别君去，<br>
韶华意气趋残暑。<br>
望星空，<br>
淡月残云，<br>
江山万里谁同路？<br>
目极青天海岸，<br>
红日朝发，<br>
敢问天，<br>
听霜露。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>长大后我就成了你</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2012年1月16日<br>
小时，没有长大后的烦恼。<br>
长大后，，没有小时的快乐。<br>
只是因为，<br>
长大后没有成为你。</p>
<p>希望啊 青春无法用尽，<br>
盼望啊 再次寻找到你。<br>
只是因为，<br>
长大后想成为你。</p>
<p>有谁能够坚守，<br>
心中的那份信念。<br>
无悔的承诺，筑起绚丽的彩练。</p>
<p>险途，使人斗志昂扬，<br>
山峰，令人一览群山。<br>
激荡于心底，<br>
只是因为，<br>
长大后我就成了你。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>         </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——由张胜利的事迹想到，送给那些辛勤追寻自己目标的人们！<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>沁园春 冬颜</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2012年1月21日晚<br>
雪漫北国，<br>
万里江山，<br>
意与谁言？<br>
叹前路漫漫，<br>
声断九天。<br>
路转峰回，<br>
今昔何年？<br>
春秋华章，<br>
冬夏依然，<br>
笑对年华泪与欢。<br>
雪龙舞，<br>
看寒意阑珊，<br>
尽在心间。</p>
<p>朝夕如此并肩，<br>
晓看春晖盼团圆。<br>
惜似水流年，<br>
又是龙颜。<br>
万家灯火，<br>
共展千年。<br>
神舟平川，<br>
雪域高原，<br>
只愿天下共相伴。<br>
细听声，<br>
那踏雪绵延，<br>
重走河山。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>清明月</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2012年清明<br>
清明明月，酌月夜，寒光浸杯盏。<br>
阳春春色，风拂面，绿意满人间。<br>
纸灰灰飞，烟灭间，化蝶坟碣连。<br>
檀香燃冉，绕九泉，归路却绵延。<br>
斟酒满杯，杜鹃啼，梦醒似昨天。<br>
看罢云烟，争朝夕，前路仍依然。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>《康熙大帝》读后</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2012年夏<br>
叶落秋风只三百，<br>
无限春光待流觞。<br>
策马奔腾随浪去，<br>
月梭云影作戎装。<br>
千古一帝传佳话，<br>
万里江山美名扬。<br>
嗟叹残年护风烛，<br>
唯有日月送流芳。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>寒梅赠友</strong><br>
唤友寻花花自休，<br>
粉红零落几时有。<br>
误入寒梅最深处，<br>
堪比桃李杏花眸。<br>
<br/><br>
<strong>时月</strong><br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>                        </mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span><span class="mspace nobreak"> </span></span></span></span>——2018年1月9日<br>
寒风长影非月明，<br>
高灯流火映苍穹。<br>
那年清风春不再，<br>
回首笑谈数星空。</p>
<p>星空本无流沙狂，<br>
残云伴影作新裳。<br>
惜逢此时已深冬，<br>
月明初探为(wéi)戎装。</p>
<p>戎装一饮进胸膛，<br>
侠肝孤胆化惆怅。<br>
待到春风柳香来，<br>
化作寒光蝶雁黄。</p>
]]></content>
